Numbers always have thousands separator in ',' and decimals in '.'
Always include thousands separator
Most numbers shouldnt have decimals showing. If the number is <100, then put a single decimal place
If number is <1, put 2 decimal places.

Percentages should be +0.0% and -0.0%
